burlap.oomdp.statehashing

Class HashableState.CachedHashableState

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.HashableState
      • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.HashableState.CachedHashableState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    State
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleHashableStateFactory.SimpleCachedHashableState
    Enclosing class:
    HashableState

    public abstract static class HashableState.CachedHashableState
extends HashableState
    A hash code cached abstract implementation of HashableState. Once a hash code is computed, it is saved so that it does not need to be used again. Implementing this class only requires implementing computeHashCode().
